<p>LeraJane,</p><p>Your replies are always so calming and helpful.  Thanks so much for being here-- I'm always excited when I see that you have posted a response to anyone about anything!</p><p>I so appreciate your reassurance-- seems like I just have to "keep on keepin' on" with the looking.  It feels natural to do so at this point.</p><p>Thanks again,</p><p>Ansley</p>
